                  <decoDesc><decoNote xml:id="d1">Ḥarag, fol. 1r</decoNote></decoDesc>
                  <additions><list><item xml:id="a1">f. 9r: partly covered by the previous quire; ff. Ir-IIIr, 54v, IVr-Vv: empty; f. IIIv: a note: ይስሐቅ፡ ህዝበ፡ አጋሜ፡ ስመ፡ አቡሁ፡ ፍቂጦር፡ - Isaac (was from ) the people of Agame; the name of his father was Fəqiṭor</item>
                     <item xml:id="e1">On front cover: ኣቡነ ይስሃቅ ዘከስዋ (᾽Abunä Yəshaq zä-Käswa)
                        on f. 1r, lower margin, written with pencil: ይስሐቅ ዘከስዋ (Yəsḥäq zä-Käswa); Käswa or Kaswa is another name of Gundä Gunde</item></list></additions>
